Paper: hep-th/0008043

Date: 2000-08-04

Title: Wess--Zumino terms and Duality

Authors: A.Smailagic, E.Spallucci

Comments: 9 pages, ReVTeX, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B489 (2000) 427-434

We show the equivalence between Stuckelberg and Wess-Zumino methods ofrestoration of gauge symmetries of the anomalous, Abelian, effective action, inarbitrary even dimensions D=2k. We present dual version of Wess-Zumino termswith the compensating field described by a Kalb-Ramond like p=2k-2 form.